column1: It was a great meet. All the lifters from Army and Navy showed great
pride in their teams and put on a great show for all in attendance at
West Point. Many lifters had huge lifts but Army was especially proud
of Trev Garner and Lisa Dugan who both set Collegiate records.
Once again thanks to Charlie Schroder (NYS chairman) and all the
judges and loaders - great job! Army was proud to retain the trophy
as top military team for a fifth straight year.
Open: Can be any age.               Junior: up to 23 (Dec 31)
